<p><a href="http://www.uniqlo.com/">UNIQLO</a> is a symbol of happy and healthy life, most of UNIQLO goods are made from 100% cotton so it's very comfortable.</p>

<p>There are several UNIQLO stores in Shanghai, but these two of them are easiest to reach and they're large enough:</p>

<h2>Grand Gateway Plaza</h2>

<ul>
<li>Address: F4 Grand Gateway Plaza, #1 Hongqiao Road</li>
<li>Metro: Line 1, Xu Jia Hui</li>
</ul>

<h2>Raffles City</h2>

<ul>
<li>Address: F3 Raffles City, #268 Middle Xi Zang Road</li>
<li>Metro: Line 1 and Line 2, People Square</li>
</ul>